\$project This software make the FTTH installation process easier.

It helps network administrator to manage QR codes of customers so that when network installer comming to customerâ€™s house they only need to capture QR code to send back to this software, this software will do all the configuration worksy.

Look how easy it is to use:

\# Get your stuff done
project.do\_stuff()
\end{quote}
